@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Welcome to the Sacrament Meeting Planner";
}
<br />
<div class="card-container">
  <div class="md:flex">
    <div class="md:shrink-0">
      <img class="card-img" src="~/img/sm2tall.jpg" alt="Church members sitting in chapel while sacrament is passed with child in foreground taking a cup of water">
    </div>
    <div class="p-8">
        Using this Sacrament Meeting Planner, you will find it is easy to add member names to a database, and select up to 4 hymns and members for each meeting from searchable drop-down lists by starting to type in the select boxes:
        <br />
        <br />
        <ul>
            <li>Up to 8 pre-programmed speakers per meeting</li>
            <li>Space for intermediate musical numbers</li>
            <li>Invocations/Benedictions</li>
            <li>Up to 4 hymns</li>
        </ul> 
        <br />
           You can search for the names by first name or last name, and hymns by number or title.
